36
00:03:23,290 --> 00:03:23,840
Government,

37
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,040
San ate a chess piece.

38
00:03:26,010 --> 00:03:27,120
Hurry up and call an ambulance!

39
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,050
Call an ambulance!

40
00:03:28,050 --> 00:03:29,490
By the time the ambulance gets here, he'll already be dead.

41
00:03:29,490 --> 00:03:30,360
Help me.

42
