79
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,330
I think it's quite good.

80
00:06:04,330 --> 00:06:05,060
Chief!

81
00:06:05,490 --> 00:06:06,120
Chief.

82
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,160
Everything is arranged.

83
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,360
Let's go!

84
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:10,700
Chief.

85
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:11,080
Yes!

86
00:06:11,150 --> 00:06:11,710
Chief.

87
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,840
