106
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,230
Alright.

107
00:07:18,410 --> 00:07:19,740
Okay, please register.

108
00:07:22,850 --> 00:07:24,650
Excuse me, where is Liu Fenfang?

109
00:07:25,140 --> 00:07:28,140
