207
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,290
Chief,

208
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:52,180
I want to fight.

209
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:53,170
I can't hold it anymore.

210
00:13:53,170 --> 00:13:54,890
How many times have I told you?

211
00:13:55,890 --> 00:13:57,570
Focusing only on big things

212
00:13:57,940 --> 00:13:59,940
is an impractical romantic notion.

213
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:03,680
Even the smallest tasks need someone to handle them.

214
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:06,040
Aren't there already people doing them?

215
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:06,940
It's not like I'm indispensable.

216
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:07,740
Du Xiangdong,

217
00:14:09,130 --> 00:14:10,790
let's not discuss this today.

218
00:14:11,050 --> 00:14:13,640
Let's talk about it after you work here for three years.

219
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:15,970
I've already worked here for three years.

220
00:14:16,590 --> 00:14:18,190
Has it been three years already?

221
00:14:18,190 --> 00:14:19,060
It's been more than that.

222
00:14:19,060 --> 00:14:21,660
I've been here for three years and four months.

223
00:14:21,890 --> 00:14:22,930
That was fast.

224
00:14:25,470 --> 00:14:27,400
Then stay for another three years.

225
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,990
You have a college degree and ability.

226
00:14:28,990 --> 00:14:31,650
Young men with ambitions do not speak of sorrow.

227
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:35,140
I'll get you a position as a section chief first.

228
00:14:35,410 --> 00:14:37,250
How's everything going with that girl?

229
00:14:37,250 --> 00:14:38,110
Treat her well.

230
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:42,130
She's the most beautiful girl in the Meat Processing Plant.

231
00:14:43,210 --> 00:14:44,410
Assemble! Assemble!

232
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,800
No more free roaming!

233
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:51,100
Here, have one of mine.

234
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,580
Have a good one.

235
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:57,510
Here.

236
00:14:59,650 --> 00:15:01,370
Let me be honest with you.

237
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:03,840
I really don't want you to leave.

238
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:07,270
Since you came, my life has become much easier.

239
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:08,770
I think

240
00:15:08,980 --> 00:15:09,910
you are a...

241
00:15:11,630 --> 00:15:14,230
You're a natural-born correctional officer.

242
00:15:14,250 --> 00:15:15,910
If it really doesn't work out,

243
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:17,600
just stay here

244
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:19,440
