One, two, three, four!

256
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:21,570
Officer Wu, Officer Du.

257
00:16:40,510 --> 00:16:41,890
I'm going to the restroom.

258
00:16:41,890 --> 00:16:42,800
Now?

259
00:16:45,050 --> 00:16:45,850
Du Xiangdong!

260
00:16:47,430 --> 00:16:48,030
Come down.

261
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,050
It looked like you.

262
00:16:58,680 --> 00:16:59,610
Long time no see.

263
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,760
