268
00:17:24,780 --> 00:17:26,240
This workplace is not bad.

269
00:17:26,569 --> 00:17:29,130
The environment in the mountains is great.

270
00:17:30,130 --> 00:17:32,130
Most importantly, the air is fresh.

271
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:33,850
It's not like where we are.

272
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,610
This Yao Binbin

273
