is suspected of theft.

274
00:17:50,260 --> 00:17:51,170
This Xu Wenguo

275
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:53,480
is suspected of intentional injury

276
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:54,400
and theft.

277
00:17:57,170 --> 00:17:57,960
Stand up.

278
00:18:00,850 --> 00:18:01,650
Move inside.

279
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:22,330
[First Prize at the Police Academy]

280
00:18:25,090 --> 00:18:27,620
Why don't you ever come to our class reunions?

281
00:18:30,890 --> 00:18:31,680
I'm busy.

282
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:33,040
Busy?

283
00:18:33,630 --> 00:18:36,810
Can you really be busier than us in the Criminal Police Team?

284
00:18:36,810 --> 00:18:38,930
